data.description: Welcome to this 4 bed, 2 1/2 bath conveniently located near the expressway, dining, and shopping. This home has some updates including  a newer roof and furnace/ac. The kitchen has been modernized with granite countertops and white cupboards. Enjoy cozy evenings by the fireplace in the living room, or relax on the deck overlooking the fenced backyard. This home has a perfect blend of comfort and convenience.
